column5: LMFA I apologize in advance for being a downer but this thing was supposed to run weeks ago The talk was of selling at 2 or 3 Never happened at all Its not that the stock wont pop someday its just that it has become a mystery story to meI cant seem to read what LMFA is up to Is it building Retracing Maybe a month from now it will still be around the same price Just cant get a read on it
LMFA Sabby might have come in picture to get Craven cheap shares by keeping price under control
